    "tree": [
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Source: Acquisitions Incorporated"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Sure, accidents happen. But they seem to happen an awful lot when Acquisitions Incorporated operatives are on the scene. Naturally, nothing ever happens when there are no witnesses left behind. But sometimes one casualty is left a little less than dead, just waiting to discover what a lucky break that accident actually was."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "You were a victim of a legal incident that was ostensibly the fault of Acquisitions Incorporated. At least that's what the local magistrate said. But before a final ruling could be handed down. Acquisitions Incorporated offered you a job! Don't know how to swing a sword? They promised to teach you! Think you have what it takes to sling spells? They've got masters who'll have you throwing fire in no time!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "With the promise of untold treasures and realms of magic and mystery just a dungeon away, you left your old life behind. Now a world of adventure is yours. Just initial here and sign here and here. Absolve Acq Inc of all former claims, and acknowledge you understand past outcomes don't guarantee future results."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Skill Proficiencies:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " Medicine, Persuasion"
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "br",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Tool Proficiencies:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " One type of artisan's tools"
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "br",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Languages:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " Any one of your choice"
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "br",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Equipment:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " One set of artisan's tools, a set of "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "fine clothes"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Value:15gp Weight:6lbs"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", and 20 gp."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Feature: Legalese"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Your experience with your local legal system has given you a firm knowledge of the ins and outs of that system. Even when the law is not on your side, you can use complex terms like "
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "em",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "ex injuria jus non oritur"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " and "
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "em",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "cogitationis poenam nemo patitur"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " to frighten people into thinking you know what you're talking about. With common folks who don't know any better, you might be able to intimidate or deceive to get favors or special treatment."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Suggested Characteristics"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Plaintiffs come in many varieties. Some are innocent bystanders who want only fair compensation for their injuries. Others are professional courtroom operatives, going to extreme lengths to appear wronged in pursuit of a large payout."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "h3",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Plaintiff Personality Trait"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "table",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "th",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "d8"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "th",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Personality Trait"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "1"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I can't believe I have a chance to join Acquisitions Incorporated! The fun I'm going to have!"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "2"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I've been wronged my entire life, and the world owes me."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "3"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I have always tried to make the best of a bad situation."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "4"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The law doesn't protect the honest and the hard working. I'm going to do whatever needs to be done to make things right."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "5"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I'm always in the wrong place at the wrong time."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "6"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "My superiors are smarter and wiser than I am. I do what I'm told."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "7"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Never pass up the opportunity to make an easy bit of coin. That's my motto."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "8"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I'm beginning to feel like the gods are not on my side."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
